      <body>
         <div type="edition">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>
                  <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan>
                  <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan>.
               <lb n="2"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name type="praenomen" key="Marcus">Mar<choice><corr>c</corr><sic>q</sic></choice>us</name>
                     <name type="gentilicium" key="Ulpius">Ulpius</name>                    
                  </persName>
               <lb n="3"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name type="cognomen" key="Primitivus">Primiti<supplied reason="omitted">v</supplied>us</name>
                  </persName>
               <lb n="4"/>
                 <persName>
                    <name type="praenomen" key="Marcus">Marco</name>
                    <name type="geniticulum" key="Ulpius">Ulp</name>
                 
               <lb n="5" break="no"/>
               
                     <name type="geniticulum" key="Ulpius">io</name>
                     <name type="cognomen" key="Secundus">Sec<choice><corr>u</corr><sic>q</sic></choice>ndo</name>
                  </persName>
               <lb n="6"/>
                  alumno suo
               <lb n="7"/>
                  bene mer
               <lb n="8" break="no"/>
                  erenti fecit
               <lb n="9"/>
                  <choice><corr>q</corr><sic>c</sic></choice>ui 
                  vix<supplied reason="omitted">i</supplied>t 
                  an<supplied reason="omitted">n</supplied>is
                  <num value="13">XIII</num>
               <lb n="10"/>
                  diebus
                  <num value="10">X</num><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/>.               
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>
               To the divine spirits. Marcus Ulpius Primitivus made (this) for his well-deserving child, 
               Marcus Ulpius Secundus, who lived for thirteen years and 10+ days.
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>
               Line 2: Common orthographic substitution of "q" for "c" in Marqus
            </p>
            <p>
               Line 3: Primitius for Primitivus, likely due to haplography
            </p>
            <p>
               Line 5: Secqndo for Secundo
            </p>
            <p>
               Line 9: cui for qui (see line 2), vixt for vixit, anis for annis
            </p>
         </div>
